[genericglass Rocks] Serving Glass: Rocks With Ice

In Mixing Glass With Ice Add:
3/4 oz [genericingredient Scotch] Glenlivet Scotch Whiskey
1 1/2 oz [genericingredient Sloe Gin] Hiram Walker Sloe Gin
Dash [genericingredient Anisette] Hiram Walker Anisette
Dash Grenadine
Dash Orange Bitters
Shake and Strain

